# Normalize line endings to LF on commit and on checkout, regardless
# of host OS. Without this, Windows tools (VS Code, Git for Windows
# with core.autocrlf=true) silently re-terminate lines as CRLF on save,
# producing large "dirty" working trees of pure line-ending churn.
# text=auto lets git decide text vs binary by content inspection.
* text=auto eol=lf
